            <title>[LU-323] Should not append index to MDT name</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-323</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Lustre: MDS mdd_obd-lustre-MDT0000-0: lustre-OST0002_UUID now active, resetting orphans&lt;/p&gt;

